  "detailed_description": "2D Owen is an arcade platformer in which you can explore 8 different worlds & experience a lot of adventures.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame features:<br />\r\n- Run, jump, and swim through many exciting levels<br />\r\n- Use Umbrella to jump, fly & shoot<br />\r\n- Fly with a Jetpack, Hang-Glider, Rocket Boots and Balloon<br />\r\n- Jump with the Pogo Stick and Bouncy Ball<br />\r\n- Ride a Cart, Rocket Rollers and Rolling Ball<br />\r\n- Explore 120 levels in 8 different worlds<br />\r\n- Defeat enemies & avoid many various obstacles<br />\r\n- Find secret locations & gain extra points",
  "about_the_game": "2D Owen is an arcade platformer in which you can explore 8 different worlds & experience a lot of adventures.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame features:<br />\r\n- Run, jump, and swim through many exciting levels<br />\r\n- Use Umbrella to jump, fly & shoot<br />\r\n- Fly with a Jetpack, Hang-Glider, Rocket Boots and Balloon<br />\r\n- Jump with the Pogo Stick and Bouncy Ball<br />\r\n- Ride a Cart, Rocket Rollers and Rolling Ball<br />\r\n- Explore 120 levels in 8 different worlds<br />\r\n- Defeat enemies & avoid many various obstacles<br />\r\n- Find secret locations & gain extra points",
